## Proposed Changes

### Backend — New `OTP` Entity & Module

#### [NEW] `otp.entity.ts`
- Fields: [id](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/auth/jwt.strategy.ts#16-21), `phoneNumber`, `otpHash` (bcrypt-hashed), `expiresAt`, `isUsed`, `attempts`, `createdAt`

#### [NEW] `otp.service.ts`
- `sendOtp(phone)` — generates 6-digit OTP, hashes it, stores it, calls Twilio SMS API
- `verifyOtp(phone, code)` — checks hash, expiry (5 min), used flag, increments attempts, marks used

#### [NEW] `otp.module.ts` — imports TypeOrmModule for OTP entity, exports OtpService

